Notes: The library's Barbour County materials include family histories, cemetery records, and histories of Eufaula. Including scattered issues of the Eufaula Daily Mail and The Eufaula Times and News. Eufaula Daily Times  (1895-1900), Eufaula Tribune (1981-1994), Eufaula Weekly Bulletin (1881-1884). Also included are Barbour County Marriage Records 1855-1928, Barbour County Orphans' Court Records 1835-1886, Barbour County Estate Records 1820-1915, Barbour County List of Registered Voters 1872-1876. The library's bound periodical holdings include Eufaula Tribune (JaN 1949 - Jun. 1951, Jan. 1952 - Dec. 1980, Jan. 1997 - Dec. 1998, Jul. 1999 - Dec. 2000, Jul. 2001 - Jun. 2007).
Source of Repository Data: Alabama Department of Archives and History
